-- Greece's Alpha says looking into acquisition of Citi's local ops 
-- By George Georgiopoulos
-- Fri Apr 25, 2014 03:46AM EDT
-- None



ATHENS, April 25 (Reuters) - Greece's fourth-largest lender Alpha Bank <ACBr.AT> said on Friday it is looking into business proposals, including the possible acquisition of the operations of Citibank <C.N> in Greece.

